{"tid":929172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安泰邪邨】18歲女安泰邨家中暈倒　昏迷送院","createTime":"2018-12-05T11:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T14:03:24.000Z","uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e50763ee61912a863357c57b6477772f808f9e61","tid":929172,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:24:32.000Z","msg":"今晨(4日)6時37分，秀茂坪安泰邨明泰樓，一名49歲姓林女子報案，指其18歲姓莫女兒在單位內暈倒，救護員接報到場，將陷入昏迷的女事主送院搶救，警方初步調查後，相信事件沒有可疑，案件列有人暈倒處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/photo/bkn-20181204081028581-1204_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181204091733\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181204%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181204081028581-1204_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181204091733&h=cd807bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女子昏迷送往聯合醫院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/bkn-20181204081028581-1204_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181204%2Fbkn-20181204081028581-1204_00822_001.html&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d10ef991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/bkn-20181204081028581-1204_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n＃安泰邪邨 ＃前石礦場 ＃惡運纏身 ＃賤人賤邨"},{"pid":"4e479dca1e0712c35d3373094686f4bd9c63d7a1","tid":929172,"uid":1672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"咩年代呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ecd5a6f96a14e23f798d21900aba5203f73d78d","tid":929172,"uid":29423,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHLw1gM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHLw1gM.png&h=d63516fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c558d213ac6f632433d3b1680d2659c599d4284","tid":929172,"uid":25221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"